dataIdInfo.idAbs:
PBS&J developed this communications Facilities database from data obtained through the Environmental Protection Agency (EPA) Envirofacts Data Warehouse (Location Reference Tables (LRT) tool. EPA LRT database was query by SIC. The attribute information provided by LRT included: name, address, city, zip, state, and geographical coordinates. The original dataset has been clipped to the Delta.

PBS&J stated (7/19/2006) in general QA/QC: "Roughly accurate to +/- 300 ft versus DOQQ."

The EPA website address is: http://www.epa.gov/enviro/html/locational/lrt/ez.html

Data provided by URS Corporation was incorporated for the state of Alaska. For each item or feature provided, a note was included under the Comment field.
